{"tid":1688232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"冇言論自由囉","createTime":"2019-11-02T10:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T11:29:17.000Z","uid":230197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1520858d9ea6ad0defc0841799f2d28020de42","tid":1688232,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"律政司司長以公眾利益守護者身份，入稟高等法院申請禁制令，禁止任何人非法於網上論壇及通訊軟件，包括連登及 telegram，發佈任何訊息或言論可促進、鼓勵或煽動其他人士威脅使用暴力，包括非法傷害他人及損壞香港的任何財物，或協助及教唆他人作出相關行為。高等法院法院今緊急開庭處理，並批下臨時禁制令，時效至下月 15 日。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道及文章：<br />\n<br />\n【網禁！】律政司入稟禁在連登、Telegram 等發佈煽動暴力言論　獲高院頒臨時禁制令<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PzuHxj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PzuHxj&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=4dd25584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PzuHxj</a><br />\n<br />\n連登回應：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2C3bjRn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2C3bjRn&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=aaa88698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2C3bjRn</a><br />\n<br />\n莫乃光：等同實施中國式防火牆　呂秉權：或如大陸被安插「莫須有」罪名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34iLNUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34iLNUw&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b00f6797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34iLNUw</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司申禁制令禁連登 Telegram 發暴力言論　網民質疑難以執行　嘲政府做法兒戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/334StFt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F334StFt&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=f756e94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/334StFt</a><br />\n<br />\n關於逐步網禁的三個疑問／林彥邦<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PySfCB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PySfCB&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=bc3a649e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PySfCB</a>"},{"pid":"eefb46fffec6736ff827a698ead4bca9aa87c233","tid":1688232,"